{"tid":2067636,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"The Hiking Serect - 檔案編號: 2020017 – 放過大澳居民啦","createTime":"2020-06-17T06:37:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T16:41:17.000Z","uid":105567,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"16debe1d3a42de53c0d66d4fae04edc522921116","tid":2067636,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:37:59.000Z","msg":"「香港行山遠足之友(吹水山谷）)版主Ming Cheung的行山態度好有問題，今次事情更涉及大澳居民利益，好過份。<br />\n<br />\n他早前帶領幾位山友到大嶼山水澇漕和萬丈布天池玩水兼開爐煮食，而開爐的地方更是水中的凸起的一塊岩石，石面不平，稍一不慎把爐翻側，食物殘渣就會隨水沖走，最大問題是由於天池為大澳及二澳居民的食用水，因此已禁止遊人戲水，沿路亦有不少橫額提示遊人，望其有公德心或責任心，違規下水者一經定罪可被罰款$5萬及監禁兩年。大家切勿以身試法！到來玩水無疑是把快樂建築於大澳居民身上。<br />\n<br />\n遊人的玩樂地方可以選擇，玩水的地方多的是，未必要到別人賴以為生的地方吧，但大澳居民受環境影響，不可選擇水源，只能依靠天池的水源維生，這種玩法非常自私，要別人飲用污染的食水。雖然有不少遊人專程到來玩水，又不止他一人犯錯，但這樣公開天池玩水的事情，想網友們有樣學樣嗎？！<br />\n<br />\n身為一個十萬人的行山群組版主，帶頭破壞環境，傷害居民，這種行為要不得。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源： <br />\n<a href=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140918/00681_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140918%2F00681_001.html&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG%2F4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=23fdc010\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/news/20140918/00681_001.html</a><br />\n <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/923321197764614/permalink/3095839503846095/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F923321197764614%2Fpermalink%2F3095839503846095%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG%2F4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=bad29bc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/923321197764614/permalink/3095839503846095/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1793097901007759/videos/262655401673248/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1793097901007759%2Fvideos%2F262655401673248%2F&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG%2F4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=a5c80995\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1793097901007759/videos/262655401673248/</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n(Admin帶頭盔：本專頁是公開的中立平台，投稿內容並不代表本專頁立場。而在&ldquo;香港行山遠足之友「吹水山谷」&rdquo;出現的資料一概不會河蟹，因為在十萬人的群組出現的東西不可能是秘密。)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=141955207494250&amp;id=105270474496057\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D141955207494250%26id%3D105270474496057&d=3WJ6yD1ie6zkJWt%2B9GiXG%2F4FZ2Hvuo87ztF5QEQ%2B7nM%3D&h=e4612729\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=141955207494250&amp;id=105270474496057</a>"},{"pid":"398d23f39efd96a7253bc96f021afb918fdd3a9c","tid":2067636,"uid":62721,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T06:46:35.000Z","msg":"係人地上游玩水,好仆街"},{"pid":"3fa2f89685be266181d392ae370705e88da0ebdf","tid":2067636,"uid":42586,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T09:21:32.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣最鐘意同啲支那大媽去行山<br />\n仲要勁撚串 加埋柒到仆街<br />\n一早已經係過街老鼠"},{"pid":"578c439faabce28dd96dd7e1bd48bb8717ba149b","tid":2067636,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XoRg2ZM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXoRg2ZM.jpg&h=f82267e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQFQ7rs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQFQ7rs.jpg&h=1b4b0cc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5Xv7rs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5Xv7rs.jpg&h=674d5300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTTLbS8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTTLbS8.jpg&h=3d654023&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a63b92a78a65dd3383ccb9dc66e7d3be1e7d8a65","tid":2067636,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:48:22.000Z","msg":"行山友大多都藍"},{"pid":"fec1a0cd597a8721b2d26e7dfccd698d275f26bd","tid":